   "source": [
    "# 3.4 前馈网络 (Feed-Forward Network)\n",
    "\n",
    "前馈网络是Transformer中注意力层之后的核心组件，负责对注意力输出进行非线性变换，增强模型的表达能力。\n",
    "\n",
    "本节涵盖：\n",
    "- SwiGLU\n",
    "- GeGLU\n",
    "- 标准FFN"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. SwiGLU\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：提升FFN的表达能力和训练稳定性\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：在标准FFN的基础上引入门控机制（Gated Linear Unit），使用Swish激活函数。公式：SwiGLU(x) = W2(SiLU(W1·x) ⊗ W3·x)，其中⊗表示逐元素乘法。\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心优势**：\n",
    "- 门控机制：W3作为"门"控制信息流，决定哪些特征应该通过\n",
    "- SiLU激活：平滑的非线性函数 x·σ(x)，梯度更平滑\n",
    "- 三矩阵结构：比标准FFN多一个权重矩阵，但表达能力显著提升\n",
    "\n",
    "**代表模型**：LLaMA、PaLM、Mistral、Qwen\n",
    "\n",
    "**参数量**：3 × d_model × d_ff（比标准FFN多50%参数，但效果更好）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class SwiGLUFFN(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d_model=128, d_ff=512):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.w1 = nn.Linear(d_model, d_ff, bias=False)\n",
    "        self.w2 = nn.Linear(d_ff, d_model, bias=False)\n",
    "        self.w3 = nn.Linear(d_model, d_ff, bias=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.w2(F.silu(self.w1(x)) * self.w3(x))\n",
    "\n",
    "ffn = SwiGLUFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "x = torch.randn(2, 16, 128)\n",
    "out = ffn(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== SwiGLU FFN ===')\n",
    "print(f'Input: {x.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'Output: {out.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'Parameters: {sum(p.numel() for p in ffn.parameters()):,}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nComputation breakdown:')\n",
    "print(f'  W1: {128}x{512} = {128*512:,} params (projection)')\n",
    "print(f'  W2: {512}x{128} = {512*128:,} params (back projection)')\n",
    "print(f'  W3: {128}x{512} = {128*512:,} params (gate)')\n",
    "print(f'  Total: {3*128*512:,} params')\n",
    "\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "    gate_values = torch.sigmoid(ffn.w1(x))\n",
    "    print(f'\\nGate statistics (SiLU gate = x * sigmoid(x)):')\n",
    "    print(f'  Sigmoid mean: {gate_values.mean():.4f}')\n",
    "    print(f'  Sigmoid std: {gate_values.std():.4f}')\n",
    "    print(f'  ~50% of features are gated through on average')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: The gate (W3) controls which features pass through,')\n",
    "print(f'making the network more expressive than standard ReLU FFN.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. GeGLU\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：GLU变体，性能优于标准ReLU FFN\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：使用GeLU替代Swish的GLU变体，公式：GeGLU(x) = W2(GeLU(W1·x) ⊗ W3·x)。\n",
    "\n",
    "**GeLU函数**：GeLU(x) = x · Φ(x)，其中Φ(x)是标准正态分布的累积分布函数\n",
    "- GeLU可以看作一种概率性的ReLU，以概率决定是否激活\n",
    "- 比ReLU更平滑，梯度更连续\n",
    "\n",
    "**与SwiGLU的区别**：\n",
    "- SwiGLU使用SiLU(x) = x · σ(x)（sigmoid加权）\n",
    "- GeGLU使用GeLU(x) = x · Φ(x)（正态CDF加权）\n",
    "- 两者效果接近，SwiGLU在LLaMA系列中更常用\n",
    "\n",
    "**代表模型**：Gemini"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class GeGLUFFN(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d_model=128, d_ff=512):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.w1 = nn.Linear(d_model, d_ff, bias=False)\n",
    "        self.w2 = nn.Linear(d_ff, d_model, bias=False)\n",
    "        self.w3 = nn.Linear(d_model, d_ff, bias=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.w2(F.gelu(self.w1(x)) * self.w3(x))\n",
    "\n",
    "ffn_geglu = GeGLUFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "ffn_swiglu = SwiGLUFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "x = torch.randn(2, 16, 128)\n",
    "\n",
    "out_geglu = ffn_geglu(x)\n",
    "out_swiglu = ffn_swiglu(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== GeGLU FFN ===')\n",
    "print(f'Input: {x.shape}, Output: {out_geglu.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'Parameters: {sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_geglu.parameters()):,}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\n=== Activation Function Comparison ===')\n",
    "t = torch.linspace(-3, 3, 100)\n",
    "silu_vals = F.silu(t)\n",
    "gelu_vals = F.gelu(t)\n",
    "relu_vals = F.relu(t)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'At x=-1: ReLU={F.relu(torch.tensor(-1.0)):.4f}, GeLU={F.gelu(torch.tensor(-1.0)):.4f}, SiLU={F.silu(torch.tensor(-1.0)):.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'At x=0:  ReLU={F.relu(torch.tensor(0.0)):.4f}, GeLU={F.gelu(torch.tensor(0.0)):.4f}, SiLU={F.silu(torch.tensor(0.0)):.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'At x=1:  ReLU={F.relu(torch.tensor(1.0)):.4f}, GeLU={F.gelu(torch.tensor(1.0)):.4f}, SiLU={F.silu(torch.tensor(1.0)):.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'At x=2:  ReLU={F.relu(torch.tensor(2.0)):.4f}, GeLU={F.gelu(torch.tensor(2.0)):.4f}, SiLU={F.silu(torch.tensor(2.0)):.4f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey differences:')\n",
    "print(f'  ReLU: hard cutoff at 0, no negative values')\n",
    "print(f'  GeLU: smooth, allows small negative values (probabilistic gating)')\n",
    "print(f'  SiLU: smooth, always positive for x>0, small negative values for x<0')\n",
    "print(f'\\nBoth GeGLU and SwiGLU outperform standard ReLU FFN significantly.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 标准FFN\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：基础的前馈网络\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：两层线性变换加ReLU激活：FFN(x) = W2·ReLU(W1·x + b1) + b2，结构简单但表达能力不如GLU变体。\n",
    "\n",
    "**特点**：\n",
    "- 两矩阵结构：仅W1和W2两个权重矩阵\n",
    "- ReLU激活：简单但存在"神经元死亡"问题\n",
    "- 参数量：2 × d_model × d_ff\n",
    "\n",
    "**与GLU变体的对比**：\n",
    "| 特性 | 标准FFN | SwiGLU/GeGLU |\n",
    "|------|---------|---------------|\n",
    "| 权重矩阵数 | 2 | 3 |\n",
    "| 激活函数 | ReLU | SiLU/GeLU |\n",
    "| 门控机制 | 无 | 有 |\n",
    "| 参数量 | 2d·d_ff | 3d·d_ff |\n",
    "| 表达能力 | 基础 | 显著更强 |\n",
    "\n",
    "**代表模型**：原始Transformer、GPT-1/2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class StandardFFN(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d_model=128, d_ff=512):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.w1 = nn.Linear(d_model, d_ff)\n",
    "        self.w2 = nn.Linear(d_ff, d_model)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.w2(F.relu(self.w1(x)))\n",
    "\n",
    "ffn_std = StandardFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "ffn_swiglu = SwiGLUFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "ffn_geglu = GeGLUFFN(d_model=128, d_ff=512)\n",
    "\n",
    "x = torch.randn(2, 16, 128)\n",
    "out_std = ffn_std(x)\n",
    "out_swiglu = ffn_swiglu(x)\n",
    "out_geglu = ffn_geglu(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== FFN Variants Comparison ===')\n",
    "print(f'Input: {x.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nStandard FFN:  params={sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_std.parameters()):,}, output={out_std.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'SwiGLU FFN:    params={sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_swiglu.parameters()):,}, output={out_swiglu.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'GeGLU FFN:     params={sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_geglu.parameters()):,}, output={out_geglu.shape}')\n",
    "\n",
    "std_params = sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_std.parameters())\n",
    "glu_params = sum(p.numel() for p in ffn_swiglu.parameters())\n",
    "print(f'\\nGLU variants use {glu_params/std_params:.1f}x more parameters but are significantly more expressive.')\n",
    "\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "    relu_out = F.relu(ffn_std.w1(x))\n",
    "    dead_neurons = (relu_out == 0).float().mean()\n",
    "    print(f'\\nReLU \"dead neuron\" ratio: {dead_neurons:.2%}')\n",
    "    print(f'(Neurons with zero output cannot learn -> gradient is zero)')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\n=== Summary ===')\n",
    "print(f'Standard: W2(ReLU(W1(x)))        -> Original Transformer, GPT-1/2')\n",
    "print(f'SwiGLU:   W2(SiLU(W1(x)) * W3(x)) -> LLaMA, PaLM, Mistral (most popular)')\n",
    "print(f'GeGLU:    W2(GeLU(W1(x)) * W3(x)) -> Gemini')\n",
    "print(f'\\nModern LLMs universally adopt GLU variants for better performance.')"
   ]
  }
